  [warning] `WaitGroup.Add` inside a `task`
   ╭─[test.lis:7:5]
 6 │   task {
 7 │     wg.Add(1)
   ·     ────┬────
   ·         ╰── may run after `Wait`
 8 │     wg.Done()
   ╰────
  help: If `Wait` runs before this `Add`, it sees a zero counter and returns immediately. Call `Add` before the `task` · code: [lint.waitgroup_add_in_task]
